{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"实体报头","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity_header","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 当前的 HTTP/1.1 规范中不再提及实体、实体报头和实体的体。这中的有些字段现在被称为表示头字段（<a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7231#section-3\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 7231, section 3: Representations</a>）。</p>\n</div>\n<p>实体报头是描述了一个 HTTP 消息有效载荷（即关于消息主体的元数据）的 HTTP 报头，见 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP_header\">HTTP header</a>。实体报头包括 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Length\"><code>Content-Length</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Language\"><code>Content-Language</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Encoding\"><code>Content-Encoding</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Type\"><code>Content-Type</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Expires\"><code>Expires</code></a> 等。实体报头可能同时存在于 HTTP 请求和响应信息中。</p>\n<p>尽管实体报头既非请求或响应报头，（由于它经常出现在请求头或响应头中）它们通常包含于此类概念中。</p>\n<p>在下面的例子中，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Length\"><code>Content-Length</code></a> 是实体报头，而 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Host\"><code>Host</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/User-Agent\"><code>User-Agent</code></a> 是请求报头。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">POST /myform.html HTTP/1.1\nHost: developer.mozilla.org\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10.9; rv:50.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/50.0\nContent-Length: 128\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多信息","title":"更多信息","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术知识","title":"技术知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers\">所有 HTTP 报头列表</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"更多信息","id":"更多信息"}],"summary":"实体报头是描述了一个 HTTP 消息有效载荷（即关于消息主体的元数据）的 HTTP 报头，见 HTTP header。实体报头包括 Content-Length、Content-Language、Content-Encoding、Content-Type 和 Expires 等。实体报头可能同时存在于 HTTP 请求和响应信息中。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Entity header","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"En-tête d'entité","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Entity header (エンティティヘッダー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"엔티티 헤더","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Cabeçalho de entidade","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Заголовок сущности","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/entity_header","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/entity_header/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity_header","title":"实体报头"}],"pageTitle":"实体报头 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}